org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd

Class CDTABLEBEGIN

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.AbstractStruct
      • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDRecord
        • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDTABLEBEGIN
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable

    public class CDTABLEBEGIN
extends CDRecord
    This structure specifies the beginning of a table. It contains information about the format and size of the table. Use this structure when accessing a table in a rich text field. As of R5, this structure is preceded by a CDPRETABLEBEGIN structure. The CDPRETABLEBEGIN structure specifies additional table properties. (editods.h)
